name: Orbiting The Blockchain - Tezos Long Play
description:
The lunarbunnies attempted to open a wormhole to another galaxy, but a miscalculation has opened a doorway to another dimension where blockchains take on a living physical form. Ego Bucks send his fleet of Starbunnies to determine what sort of utility they offer.

Video NFTs, each representing different cryptocoins. The soundtrack was developed especially for this series.

This is the long play version of the Tezos Edition with a three minute loop. A separate one minute short play edition is also available.

I would like to take the opportunity to raise some money for charitable causes so some of the proceeds from the sale of this work will be donated. You can find out more on the charities page of my lunarbunnies.com website.
